{"tid":1814420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實屌勇武退場做乜鳩？","createTime":"2020-01-07T02:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T05:19:21.000Z","uid":181474,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db7d9c7eb0df4b9c73845ad5a85c500ffd65b188","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"如果係手足開嘅，你再屌佢哋就真係變condom<br />\n如果係五毛開嘅，你屌佢嘅時候，同時旁敲側擊咁比說話勇武聽，咁你咪中撚咗五毛計囉<br />\n<br />\n唔好再講&ldquo;邊有真勇武會上連登開po放負&rdquo;<br />\n成件事唔係靠屌五毛就可以處理，依家係要比勇武對行動有返啲信心，比個低risk嘅環境勇武發揮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">冷處理啊屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"33a1d18fb46bd2688b5c56227e18ff098866a5a9","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44b9f0e744782a3b2ebf576a8563a4024919770e","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d2c8cd1f0a193369d79831aec704249a4ce4cf6","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:04:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d26da2bd6e2e000603ff9f2b4620e72a0d1b4ad","tid":1814420,"uid":9394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"講到尾 大家心理質素真係要高<br />\n唔好人地講幾句野就灰 勇武和理都係<br />\n同時都唔好唔諗清楚就行動 捉鬼就係無諗清楚"},{"pid":"368466ef0886448f8b8906adfa57ba2fd9035fe3","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aea25368c9cbd6b126e25b17d41bbf1e628a913","tid":1814420,"uid":93124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:07:43.000Z","msg":"[長文] 要革命，請先革了自己的命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eJFHRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eJFHRS</a>"},{"pid":"93d34f34e9955a9d6a7a3d918bfa415b9fbafb66","tid":1814420,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"突發！和勇全面退場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814289</a>"},{"pid":"c4f767e3f2e405b3c27b1a00bcd93c887e6bd733","tid":1814420,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"冷你老母<br />\n又用蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fafe8d47f5dcbcf956f981000fe135c609848fa","tid":1814420,"uid":270798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:24:19.000Z","msg":"勇武係抗爭，唔係送頭。<br />\n係人都會攰，攰就要休息，好正常<br />\n勇武都係人，抗爭左七個月<br />\n雖然唔可以話一事無成，但離勝利真係好遠<br />\n當然自中共立國以黎，從未有過比呢兩年更好的時機，中共面對國內經濟壓力及香港抗爭造成的全世界政治壓力，我地真係有機會迫到中共響不情願之下讓步。<br />\n呢個可能性係好多勇武身心受傷/被控告/坐監甚至被失蹤被殺換返黎，絕對唔可以忘記。<br />\n<br />\n勇武休息過後，如果認為抗爭仍要繼續，自然會再出黎。"},{"pid":"e6fe28825261f4765d962aaed77349094a2b8a57","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:34:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86cac667853c4572c547ec1e5a17125c5ab371c4","tid":1814420,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"退場都要捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78818758eae84fa55db499a4e1ad272515479c94","tid":1814420,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n低調處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025288e9a9edd53de10ba8d57a45f4ee711a3181","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78818758eae84fa55db499a4e1ad272515479c94","tid":1814420,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"冷處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n低調處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"sor鳩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5b1b1c3dd17c2d2fe549fe2b891601de934100","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d50902dbea431c04bdc24278b7650aea73ecccbe","tid":1814420,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}